    "description": "<strong>SANRI</strong>, 是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏，您将扮演一位妻子在野营期间失踪的精神分裂症角色。面对妄想，解开谜团，尽管你的时空感不断扭曲，但仍要努力找到它。<br><br><u>重要提示：游戏不会用太多提示来引导你，它专注于探索。考虑到游戏在这方面可能是一场困难的比赛。</u><br><br><strong>故事</strong><br>如果你和你的伴侣在一个愉快的夜晚露营后醒来，却看不到他们在你身边，你会怎么做？拿起你的手电筒，潜入森林深处寻找它。你的精神分裂妄想和错觉永远不会离开你。尽管如此，你能找到他吗？<br><br><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br>你的敌人会以你的恐惧为食。逃跑或面对它。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/896d852037a671b2e7f4b2896d6a06bd.poster.avif?t=1743319558\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/896d852037a671b2e7f4b2896d6a06bd.webm?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/896d852037a671b2e7f4b2896d6a06bd.mp4?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>对付妄想的方法是通过抗精神病药物。始终随身携带。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/bb5dcefb66bd54dd51dfebdd4c5a7e79.poster.avif?t=1743319558\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/bb5dcefb66bd54dd51dfebdd4c5a7e79.webm?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/bb5dcefb66bd54dd51dfebdd4c5a7e79.mp4?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>适应不断变化的时间和地点。探索幽灵般的环境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/436d3b93c6982ffc03cc0357779ae295.poster.avif?t=1743319558\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/436d3b93c6982ffc03cc0357779ae295.webm?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/436d3b93c6982ffc03cc0357779ae295.mp4?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过您拍摄的照片重温回忆并寻找神秘线索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/fb72c7b248a4eb46875ede781635da38.poster.avif?t=1743319558\" width=598 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/fb72c7b248a4eb46875ede781635da38.webm?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/fb72c7b248a4eb46875ede781635da38.mp4?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>检查物体并与之互动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/014ba16b7ffb2f73c1f5d7a37f04e1cb.poster.avif?t=1743319558\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/014ba16b7ffb2f73c1f5d7a37f04e1cb.webm?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137660/extras/014ba16b7ffb2f73c1f5d7a37f04e1cb.mp4?t=1743319558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
